EDGE CASES AND TESTS
Input                   Expected Output
"Hello $USER"	        "Hello alice"
'Hello $USER'	        'Hello $USER'
"Path is $PATH/bin"	    "Path is /usr/bin:/bin/bin"
"$"	                    "" (empty string or preserved as literal)
"$UNDEFINED"	        ""
"Mix$VAR1and$VAR2"	    "Mixval1andval2"

